 <div class=\"container\"> <a class=\"navbar-brand title font-weight-lighter\" href=\"/folio-portfolio/\"> <span class=\"font-weight-bold\">Виталий</span> Азаров </a> <button class=\"navbar-toggler collapsed ml-auto\" type=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#navbarNav\" aria-controls=\"navbarNav\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\"> <span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle navigation</span> <span class=\"icon-bar top-bar\"></span> <span class=\"icon-bar middle-bar\"></span> <span class=\"icon-bar bottom-bar\"></span> </button> <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse text-right\" id=\"navbarNav\"> <ul class=\"navbar-nav ml-auto flex-nowrap\"> <li class=\"nav-item \"> <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/folio-portfolio/\">обо мне </a> </li> <li class=\"nav-item active\"> <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/\">проекты <span class=\"sr-only\">(current)</span> </a> </li> <li class=\"nav-item\"> <button id=\"search-toggle\" title=\"Search\" onclick=\"openSearchModal()\"> <span class=\"nav-link\">ctrl k <i class=\"fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass\"></i></span> </button> </li> <li class=\"toggle-container\"> <button id=\"light-toggle\" title=\"Change theme\"> <i class=\"fa-half-sun-moon\" id=\"light-toggle-system\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-moon\" id=\"light-toggle-dark\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-sun\" id=\"light-toggle-light\"></i> </button> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </nav> <progress id=\"progress\" value=\"0\" max=\"1392\" style=\"top: 63px;\"> <div class=\"progress-container\"> <span class=\"progress-bar\"></span> </div> </progress> </header> <div class=\"container mt-5\" role=\"main\"> <div class=\"post\"> <header class=\"post-header\"> <h1 class=\"post-title\">проекты</h1> <p class=\"post-description\">Мои проекты по веб-безопасности, ИИ/МЛ и разработке.</p> </header> <article> <div class=\"projects\"> <a id=\"веб-безопасность\" href=\".#%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%B1-%D0%B1%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%BF%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D1%8C\"> <h2 class=\"category\">веб-безопасность</h2> </a> <div class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3\"> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/1_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/host-header-injection.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">HTTP Host Header Injection</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">Наглядный разбор и демо уязвимости Host Header Injection</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> <a id=\"ии-мл\" href=\".#%D0%B8%D0%B8-%D0%BC%D0%BB\"> <h2 class=\"category\">ии-мл</h2> </a> <div class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3\"> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/2_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/rag-terminal.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">Embedding</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">Интерактивный стенд для экспериментов с эмбеддингами и семантическим поиском</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/3_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/chunking-embeddings-explained.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">Embedding Chunks</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">Интерактивная визуализация, которая показывает почему нельзя пихать весь текст в один эмбеддинг и как правильный чанкинг улучшает поиск</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> <a id=\"инфраструктура\" href=\".#%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%84%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%81%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D0%BA%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0\"> <h2 class=\"category\">инфраструктура</h2> </a> <div class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3\"> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/6_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/dark-infrastructure.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">DARK — Сетевая инфраструктура</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">Образовательная платформа для изучения сетевой инфраструктуры Dark Web: Tor, SOCKS5, I2P, Onion-сервисы</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> <a id=\"разное\" href=\".#%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B5\"> <h2 class=\"category\">разное</h2> </a> <div class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3\"> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/4_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/ecommerce-generator.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">E-Commerce Генератор</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">Генератор готовых карточек товаров для маркетплейсов — Wildberries, Ozon, Яндекс Маркет</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> <div class=\"col\"> <a href=\"/folio-portfolio/projects/5_project/\"> <div class=\"card h-100 hoverable\"> <figure> <picture>  <img src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/img/projects/ai-searcher.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"project thumbnail\" loading=\"eager\" onerror=\"this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();\"> </picture> </figure> <div class=\"card-body\"> <h2 class=\"card-title\">AI-Searcher</h2> <p class=\"card-text\">AI-поисковик с академическим поиском, анализом источников и интеллектуальным чатом</p> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> </div> </article> </div> </div> <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.0/dist/jquery.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script> <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mdbootstrap@4.20.0/js/mdb.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-NdbiivsvWt7VYCt6hYNT3h/th9vSTL4EDWeGs5SN3DA=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/masonry-layout@4.2.2/dist/masonry.pkgd.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-Nn1q/fx0H7SNLZMQ5Hw5JLaTRZp0yILA/FRexe19VdI=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/imagesloaded@5.0.0/imagesloaded.pkgd.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-htrLFfZJ6v5udOG+3kNLINIKh2gvoKqwEhHYfTTMICc=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/masonry.js?v=a0db7e5d5c70cc3252b3138b0c91dcaf\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/medium-zoom@1.1.0/dist/medium-zoom.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-ZgMyDAIYDYGxbcpJcfUnYwNevG/xi9OHKaR/8GK+jWc=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/zoom.js?v=85ddb88934d28b74e78031fd54cf8308\"></script> <script src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/no_defer.js?v=2781658a0a2b13ed609542042a859126\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/common.js?v=c15de51d4bb57887caa2c21988d97279\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/copy_code.js?v=c8a01c11a92744d44b093fc3bda915df\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script> <script defer=\"\" src=\"/folio-portfolio/assets/js/jupyt